short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extract contact from current web page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This application helps recruiters in their daily work, it monitors activity on all sites when you are working and it is turned on. This allows you to restore your work history with a full understanding of where and what resources you were on. And now, at the click of a button, it sends the contents of the page for further parsing and extracting information about the applicant from it.
